{"id":73468,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/05/玉树全貌/","date":"2010-05-18T12:40:05Z","modified":"2010-05-21T04:39:50Z","title":"安猪: 玉树全貌（图）","content":"<h1>17 May 10 <a id=\"post-1317\" title=\"Permanent Link to 玉树全貌\" rel=\"bookmark\" href=\"http://anzhu.net/2010/05/17/%e7%8e%89%e6%a0%91%e5%85%a8%e8%b2%8c/\">玉树全貌</a></h1>\n<p>今天爬山时所拍。可以清晰地看到汽车站、求松家（我住的地方）、格萨尔王广场、结古寺。</p>\n<p>照片中左边到中央靠山的房子全塌了。</p>\n<p>点击查看原图，需翻墙。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://twitpic.com/1olz8s/full\"><img src=\"http://anzhu.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/yushu.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"yushu.jpg\" width=\"551\" height=\"81\" /></a></p>\n<p>在山顶上，用3G连线开会，对面是结古寺。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://anzhu.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/r0016180.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"R0016180.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<p>结古寺外，掉了顶的白塔和完好的白塔相映成趣。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://anzhu.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/r0016193.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"R0016193.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<p>结古寺下成群的救灾帐篷，但远处的云彩更加瑰丽──如果我们看不到希望，那才是真正的灾民。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://anzhu.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/r0016195.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"R0016195.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<div>Filed in <a title=\"View all posts in 旅行记\" rel=\"category tag\" href=\"http://anzhu.net/category/%e6%97%85%e8%a1%8c%e8%ae%b0/\">旅行记</a></div>\n<div>\n<div>« <a href=\"http://anzhu.net/2010/05/16/%e7%8e%89%e6%a0%91%e6%80%a5%e9%9c%80%e8%8d%af%e5%93%81%ef%bc%81/\">玉树急需药品！</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><!-- You can start editing here. --> <!-- If comments are open, but there are no comments. --></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[10466,20534],"tags":[9595,8795,8643]}